channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Doocy Nails WH on Cover-Up of Biden's Decline, As Their Answers Just Make Everything Worse
5 key takeaways of Biden's address to the nation from the Oval Office
item.description: President Biden used his address to the nation from the Oval Office Wednesday to explain why he stepped aside from the 2024 presidential race.

item.title: Robert Wilkie to Newsmax: WH, Dems Disrespected Netanyahu
item.description: The Biden administration showed "the ultimate level of diplomatic disrespect" to Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu as he arrived in Washington this week to speak to Congress, former Secretary of Veterans Affairs Robert Wilkie told Newsmax on Thursday.

item.title: Do Ballot Initiatives Align with America’s Founding Principles?
Election integrity group dishes out $50K to whistleblowers, 6-figure Olympics ad buy: 'We're watching'
item.description: A new election integrity group says it has begun paying out whistleblowers who have noticed voting irregularities and the group is also launching a six-figure ad buy.

item.title: Texas Judge Permits Woman's Lawsuit on Murder Charge for Abortion
item.description: A Texas woman who was jailed and charged with murder after self-managing an abortion in 2022 can move forward with her lawsuit against the local sheriff and prosecutors over the case that drew national outrage before the charges were quickly dropped.

item.title: The Look on Jill Biden's Face During Joe's Speech Says Everything
House Dem from border district dodges questions on Harris' immigration record: 'Was she a border czar?'
item.description: Democratic Rep. Vicente Gonzalez declined to answer this week when asked about the job Vice President Kamala Harris did at the southern border after being tapped by President Biden to work on the issue.

item.title: DNC Scrambles for Convention After Historic Late Switch to Harris
item.description: After nearly a near year of careful planning, organizers of the Democratic National Convention are in a mad dash to accommodate a new nominee, a re-crafted program and a highly compressed deadline to pull everything off as though this was the plan all along.

item.title: Report: Leak Reveals More About Why Obama Hasn't Endorsed Harris
House Republicans replace American flags at Union Station after anti-Israel protests
item.description: House Speaker Mike Johnson led Republican lawmakers in replacing American flags that were removed and burned at Union Station during anti-Israel protests.

item.title: Emerson Poll: Trump Edges Harris in 4 Key Swing States
item.description: Former President Donald Trump leads Vice President Kamala Harris in four key battleground states and the candidates are tied in Wisconsin in a hypothetical election matchup, according to the latest survey by Emerson College Polling/The Hill.

item.title: Biden says ‘The choice is up to you, the American people’ while saying he won't seek re-election
item.description: Lame duck President Biden gave a small endorsement to Vice President Kamala Harris and did not mention former President Trump by name while saying he would not seek re-election.

item.title: Trump Urges Quick End to War on Hamas, Return of Hostages
item.description: Republican presidential nominee Donald Trump, one day before meeting Israel's Benjamin Netanyahu, called for a quick end to its war with Hamas and a return of the hostages, adding that Israel has to better manage its "public relations."
